source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_000<tab>The pedestal you see beside me is one of the pieces originally crafted for Master Nanapasi's most elaborate Little Ladies' Day doll display.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_000<tab>Bon<var 08 E3E90C0D ((<var 08 E3E90C05 ((soir)) ((jour)) /var>)) ((<var 08 E3E90C12 ((jour)) ((soir)) /var>)) /var><var 1D /var>! Le présentoir que vous voyez à côté de moi est un prototype de celui destiné à l'exposition de poupées grandeur nature.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_001<tab>Though it was eventually abandoned in favor of another design, my master wished not to see it go to waste, and thus offered to place it here, that it might be used freely by one and all.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_001<tab>Le seigneur Nanapasi, trouvant dommage qu'on le détruise, a demandé qu'il soit placé ici afin de permettre aux aventuriers de l'utiliser librement.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_002<tab>This pedestal is provided free of charge to all adventurers. Use it when taking commemorative pictures, or however you may see fit!
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_002<tab>Ce présentoir est destiné à prendre des captures d'écran ou simplement à s'amuser.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>Make use of the pedestal as often as you like, but please be considerate of other adventurers who may be waiting for their turn.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_003<tab>Veillez à ne pas le monopoliser trop longtemps si d'autres personnes attendent leur tour pour l'utiliser.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_100<tab>A doll of such size and painstaking craftsmanship that it could be easily mistaken for a living being stands atop the pedestal.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_SYSTEM_000_100<tab>Cette poupée est si détaillée qu'on la prendrait pour un être humain...

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_200<tab>Greetings, adventurer. As you might have observed, my master has grand plans for this year's Little Ladies' Day─plans that I fear have hit something of a snag. Your services would be greatly welcome, should you be willing to offer them.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_200<tab>Mon maître a conçu un projet dans l'esprit de la fête des demoiselles, mais il se heurte à certaines difficultés, et a besoin d'aide... Je m'en remets à votre bienveillance, ô aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_201<tab>Your efforts will doubtless go far in making this Little Ladies' Day one to remember. On behalf of Master Nanapasi, I offer our most sincere gratitude.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_201<tab>Mon maître Nanapasi souhaite faire plaisir à sa fille en reproduisant un décor traditionnel de la fête des demoiselles. Je compte sur votre aide bien<var 16 /var>veil<var 16 /var>lan<var 16 /var>te, ô aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>.

source: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_202<tab>In all the years I have served this family, I had never seen Master Nanapasi and Miss Ninimo so happy until this day. This would not have been possible without you, adventurer, and for that I thank you deeply.
target: TEXT_FESPDYPLAYERALTAR_00254_MAIDPDY2015_000_202<tab>Je crois bien que mon maître et sa fille ont enfin réussi à se comprendre mu<var 16 /var>tuel<var 16 /var>le<var 16 /var>ment<var 1D /var>! Je suis si heureuse pour eux que j'en ai les larmes aux yeux. Merci du fond du cœur, ô aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var>.
